flowchart TD
    Start([Fork & Clone Repository]) --> Setup[Development Setup]
    Setup --> SetupSteps[Install Erlang/OTP 28.3.1+<br/>Install rebar3<br/>Run tests]

    SetupSteps --> Check{Existing Issue?}
    Check -->|Yes| Assign[Request Assignment]
    Check -->|No| Create[Create Feature Request<br/>or Bug Report]

    Assign --> Branch[Create Feature Branch]
    Create --> Branch

    Branch --> Dev[Development Phase]
    Dev --> DevSteps[Write Tests First<br/>(Chicago School TDD)<br/>Implement Feature<br/>Run Quality Gates]

    DevSteps --> Quality{Quality Gates Pass?}
    Quality -->|No| Fix[Fix Issues]
    Fix --> Dev

    Quality -->|Yes| Docs[Update Documentation]
    Docs --> Commit[Commit Changes]

    Commit --> Push[Push to Fork]
    Push --> PR[Create Pull Request]

    PR --> Review{Review Process}
    Review --> ReviewSteps[Automated Checks<br/>Code Review<br/>CI/CD Pipeline<br/>Test Coverage]

    ReviewSteps --> ReviewPass{All Checks Pass?}
    ReviewPass -->|No| Revise[Make Revisions]
    Revise --> Push

    ReviewPass -->|Yes| Approve[Request Approval]
    Approve --> Merge[Squash & Merge]

    Merge --> Release[Next Release Cycle]
    Release --> Credit[Contributors List]

